snippet.title: Yasmin Nelson
snippet.description:
Heyaaaa! I'm Yas, often mistaken for YAAASSSSSS. 
I love a good burger or seventeen, talking nonsense, comedy, and I dream of the day where I can paint my nails without stuffing it up. 
I have the luck of a person that gets shat on by a bird right after I just stepped in dog shit, and it shows.
